===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*steyh₂-}}
From a regional use<ref>{{R:Duden|Stein}}</ref> of {{der|en|de|Stein||stone}}. Probably a clipping of {{m|de|Steingut||stoneware}} or {{m|de|Steinkrug||stone pitcher}}. Compare {{cog|ang|stǣna||stone jug, a pot of stone or earth}}. {{doublet|en|stone}}. More at {{m|en|stean}}.

